        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_ECLIPSE5UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "Ut Incendiarius, ludum in Eclipse 5 vel altiore vince, AUT ludum in Typhoon vince (Starstorm 2 necessarium).",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_ECLIPSE8UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Incendiarius: Superstes",
